Invocation Name: sri naga sai live
des:
Listen to Sri Naga Sai Mandir, Coimbatore live audio stream. By Sri Naga Sai Trust, Coimbatore. This skill presents 24 / 7 live audio streams from Saibaba temple, Coimbatore. spiritual discussions, teachings and devotional bhajans, Live Aarthi, Live bhajans and immerse yourself in devotion of Saibaba. 

The skill content is in Tamil language.

To start the darshan, just say "Alexa, play srinagasai live" or "Alexa, launch srinagasai live". At anytime, you can stop the radio by saying "Alexa, stop"
